{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":786,"text":"Every group of female friends\nhas the funny one,"},{"time":4403,"text":"the one you go to\nwhen you need a good cry,"},{"time":7166,"text":"the one who tells you to suck it up\nwhen you've had a hard day."},{"time":10841,"text":"And this group was no different."},{"time":13524,"text":"Except that this was a community\nof groundbreaking women"},{"time":17203,"text":"who came together --"},{"time":18480,"text":"first to become teammates,\nthen friends, and then family --"},{"time":22003,"text":"in the least likely of places:"},{"time":24548,"text":"on the Special Operations battlefield."},{"time":27765,"text":"This was a group of women\nwhose friendship and valor was cemented"},{"time":31026,"text":"not only by what they had seen\nand done at the tip of the spear,"},{"time":35508,"text":"but by the fact that they were there"},{"time":37503,"text":"at a time when women --\nofficially, at least --"},{"time":40045,"text":"remained banned from ground combat,"},{"time":42604,"text":"and America had no idea they existed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47546,"text":"This story begins\nwith Special Operations leaders,"},{"time":50432,"text":"some of the most tested men\nin the United States military, saying,"},{"time":54033,"text":"\"We need women to help us wage this war.\""},{"time":58358,"text":"\"America would never kill its way\nto the end of its wars,\" it argued."},{"time":61771,"text":"\"Needed more knowledge\nand more understanding.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":64763,"text":"And as everyone knows,"},{"time":66243,"text":"if you want to understand what's happening\nin a community and in a home,"},{"time":69814,"text":"you talk to women,"},{"time":71411,"text":"whether you're talking about\nSouthern Afghanistan,"},{"time":74125,"text":"or Southern California."},{"time":76558,"text":"But in this case,\nmen could not talk to women,"},{"time":79154,"text":"because in a conservative\nand traditional society like Afghanistan,"},{"time":82577,"text":"that would cause grave offense."},{"time":84809,"text":"So you needed women soldiers out there."},{"time":89045,"text":"That meant, at this time in the war,\nthat the women who would be recruited"},{"time":93042,"text":"to serve alongside Army Rangers\nand Navy SEALs,"},{"time":95929,"text":"would be seeing the kind of combat\nexperienced by less than five percent"},{"time":100413,"text":"of the entire United States military."},{"time":103579,"text":"Less than five percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106587,"text":"So the call went out."},{"time":108145,"text":"\"Female soldiers:\nBecome a part of history."},{"time":110580,"text":"Join Special Operations\non the battlefield in Afghanistan.\""},{"time":114727,"text":"This is in 2011."},{"time":116525,"text":"And from Alabama to Alaska,"},{"time":118738,"text":"a group of women who had always\nwanted to do something that mattered"},{"time":122695,"text":"alongside the best of the best,"},{"time":124697,"text":"and to make a difference\nfor their country,"},{"time":126974,"text":"answered that call to serve."},{"time":130294,"text":"And for them it was not about politics,\nit was about serving with purpose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136858,"text":"And so, the women who came\nto North Carolina"},{"time":139340,"text":"to compete for a spot on these teams"},{"time":142067,"text":"which would put women\non the Special Operations front lines,"},{"time":145288,"text":"landed and found\nvery quickly a community,"},{"time":148659,"text":"the likes of which they had never seen."},{"time":151304,"text":"Full of women who were as fierce\nand as fit as they were,"},{"time":154896,"text":"and as driven to make a difference."},{"time":157128,"text":"They didn't have to apologize\nfor who they were,"},{"time":159591,"text":"and in fact, they could celebrate it."},{"time":162589,"text":"And what they found when they were there\nwas that all of a sudden,"},{"time":166706,"text":"there were lots of people like them."},{"time":169501,"text":"As one of them said,"},{"time":170890,"text":"\"It was like you looked\naround and realized"},{"time":172960,"text":"there was more\nthan one giraffe at the zoo.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":177212,"text":"Among this team of standouts was Cassie,"},{"time":179953,"text":"a young woman who managed to be\nan ROTC cadet, a sorority sister"},{"time":184447,"text":"and a Women's Studies minor,\nall in one person."},{"time":188385,"text":"Tristan, a West Point track star,\nwho always ran and road marched"},{"time":192995,"text":"with no socks,"},{"time":194256,"text":"and had shoes whose smell proved it."},{"time":196430,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":197897,"text":"Amber, a Heidi look-alike, who had\nalways wanted to be in the infantry,"},{"time":201895,"text":"and when she found out\nthat women couldn't be,"},{"time":204395,"text":"she decided to become an intel officer."},{"time":207626,"text":"She served in Bosnia,"},{"time":208880,"text":"and later helped the FBI\nto bust drug gangs in Pennsylvania."},{"time":212979,"text":"And then there was Kate,\nwho played high school football"},{"time":216482,"text":"all four years,"},{"time":217718,"text":"and actually wanted to drop out\nafter the first,"},{"time":220324,"text":"to go into the glee club,"},{"time":221825,"text":"but when boys told her\nthat girls couldn't play football,"},{"time":224732,"text":"she decided to stay"},{"time":226013,"text":"for all the little girls\nwho would come after her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230268,"text":"For them, biology had shaped\npart of their destiny,"},{"time":232973,"text":"and put, as Cassie once said,"},{"time":235079,"text":"\"everything noble\nout of reach for girls.\""},{"time":238353,"text":"And yet, here was a chance\nto serve with the best of the best"},{"time":241673,"text":"on a mission that mattered\nto their country,"},{"time":243757,"text":"not despite the fact\nthat they were female,"},{"time":246456,"text":"but because of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248769,"text":"This team of women, in many ways,\nwas like women everywhere."},{"time":252760,"text":"They wore makeup, and in fact,"},{"time":254355,"text":"they would bond in the ladies' room\nover eyeliner and eye pencil."},{"time":258531,"text":"They also wore body armor."},{"time":260543,"text":"They would put 50 pounds\nof weight on their backs,"},{"time":262955,"text":"and board the helicopter for an operation,"},{"time":265005,"text":"and they would come back and watch\na movie called \"Bridesmaids.\""},{"time":268061,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":269936,"text":"They even wore a thing called Spanx,"},{"time":272669,"text":"because, as they found very quickly,"},{"time":274633,"text":"the uniforms made for men were\nbig where they should be small,"},{"time":278549,"text":"and small where they should be big."},{"time":280623,"text":"So Lane, an Iraq War veteran --\nyou see her here on my left --"},{"time":284184,"text":"decided she was going to go on Amazon"},{"time":286264,"text":"and order a pair of Spanx to her base,"},{"time":288407,"text":"so that her pants would fit better\nwhen she went out on mission each night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292822,"text":"These women would get together\nover video conference"},{"time":295247,"text":"from all around Afghanistan\nfrom their various bases,"},{"time":297728,"text":"and they would talk about what it was like"},{"time":299760,"text":"to be one of the only women\ndoing what they were doing."},{"time":302435,"text":"They would swap jokes,"},{"time":303636,"text":"they would talk about\nwhat was working, what wasn't,"},{"time":306112,"text":"what they had learned to do well,\nwhat they needed to do better."},{"time":309183,"text":"And they would talk about\nsome of the lighter moments of being women"},{"time":312630,"text":"out on the Special Operations front lines,"},{"time":315146,"text":"including the Shewee,"},{"time":316535,"text":"which was a tool\nthat let you pee like a guy,"},{"time":318874,"text":"although it's said to have had only\na 40 percent accuracy rate out there."},{"time":323326,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326441,"text":"These women lived in the \"and.\""},{"time":329139,"text":"They proved you could be fierce\nand you could be feminine."},{"time":332325,"text":"You could wear mascara and body armor."},{"time":335221,"text":"You could love CrossFit,\nand really like cross-stitch."},{"time":339301,"text":"You could love to climb out of helicopters\nand you could also love to bake cookies."},{"time":344578,"text":"Women live in the and every single day,"},{"time":348031,"text":"and these women brought that\nto this mission as well."},{"time":352547,"text":"On this life and death battlefield\nthey never forgot"},{"time":355466,"text":"that being female may have brought them\nto the front lines,"},{"time":358581,"text":"but being a soldier is what would\nprove themselves there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362272,"text":"There was the night Amber went\nout on mission,"},{"time":364460,"text":"and in talking to the women of the house,"},{"time":366454,"text":"realized that there was\na barricaded shooter lying in wait"},{"time":369303,"text":"for the Afghan and American forces\nwho were waiting to enter the home."},{"time":373418,"text":"Another night it was Tristan\nwho found out"},{"time":376237,"text":"that there were pieces\nthat make up explosives"},{"time":378425,"text":"all around the house\nin which they were standing,"},{"time":380746,"text":"and that in fact, explosives lay\nall the way between there"},{"time":383549,"text":"and where they were\nabout to head that night."},{"time":386061,"text":"There was the night another one\nof their teammates proved herself"},{"time":389156,"text":"to a decidedly skeptical team of SEALs,"},{"time":391647,"text":"when she found the intel item\nthey were looking for"},{"time":394067,"text":"wrapped up in a baby's wet diaper."},{"time":397309,"text":"And there was the night that Isabel,\nanother one of their teammates,"},{"time":400570,"text":"found the things\nthat they were looking for,"},{"time":402692,"text":"and received an Impact Award\nfrom the Rangers"},{"time":404832,"text":"who said that without her,"},{"time":406582,"text":"the things and the people\nthey were looking for that night"},{"time":409360,"text":"would never have been found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411553,"text":"That night and so many others,"},{"time":413405,"text":"they went out to prove themselves,\nnot only for one another,"},{"time":416520,"text":"but for everybody\nwho would come after them."},{"time":419519,"text":"And also for the men\nalongside whom they served."},{"time":423209,"text":"We talk a lot about how\nbehind every great man is a good woman."},{"time":428354,"text":"And in this case,"},{"time":429535,"text":"next to these women stood men\nwho wanted to see them succeed."},{"time":433666,"text":"The Army Ranger who trained them\nhad served 12 deployments."},{"time":437406,"text":"And when they told him\nthat he had to go train girls,"},{"time":440424,"text":"he had no idea what to expect."},{"time":443361,"text":"But at the end of eight days with these\nwomen in the summer of 2011,"},{"time":447715,"text":"he told his fellow Ranger,\n\"We have just witnessed history."},{"time":452160,"text":"These may well be\nour own Tuskegee Airmen.\""},{"time":457666,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":464390,"text":"At the heart of this team\nwas the one person"},{"time":467040,"text":"who everyone called \"the best of us.\""},{"time":469675,"text":"She was a petite blonde dynamo,"},{"time":472164,"text":"who barely reached five-foot-three."},{"time":474772,"text":"And she was this wild mix\nof Martha Stewart,"},{"time":477927,"text":"and what we know as G.I. Jane."},{"time":480665,"text":"She was someone who loved\nto make dinner for her husband,"},{"time":483513,"text":"her Kent State ROTC sweetheart\nwho pushed her to be her best,"},{"time":487640,"text":"and to trust herself,"},{"time":488993,"text":"and to test every limit she could."},{"time":491944,"text":"She also loved to put 50 pounds of weight\non her back and run for miles,"},{"time":496138,"text":"and she loved to be a soldier."},{"time":499080,"text":"She was somebody who had a bread maker\nin her office in Kandahar,"},{"time":502338,"text":"and would bake a batch of raisin bread,\nand then go to the gym"},{"time":505294,"text":"and bust out 25 or 30 pull-ups\nfrom a dead hang."},{"time":509092,"text":"She was the person who, if you needed\nan extra pair of boots"},{"time":512017,"text":"or a home-cooked dinner,\nwould be on your speed dial."},{"time":515404,"text":"Because she never, ever would talk to you"},{"time":517666,"text":"about how good she was,"},{"time":518841,"text":"but let her character speak\nthrough action."},{"time":522450,"text":"She was famous for taking the hard right\nover the easy wrong."},{"time":528487,"text":"And she was also famous\nfor walking up to a 15-foot rope,"},{"time":531901,"text":"climbing it using only her arms,"},{"time":534085,"text":"and then shuffling away and apologizing,"},{"time":536110,"text":"because she knew she was supposed\nto use both her arms and her legs,"},{"time":539524,"text":"as the Rangers had trained them."},{"time":541245,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":543145,"text":"Some of our heroes return home\nto tell their stories."},{"time":547346,"text":"And some of them don't."},{"time":549958,"text":"And on October 22, 2011,"},{"time":552527,"text":"First Lieutenant Ashley White was killed\nalongside two Rangers,"},{"time":556119,"text":"Christopher Horns"},{"time":557498,"text":"and Kristoffer Domeij."},{"time":559998,"text":"Her death threw this program built\nfor the shadows"},{"time":563271,"text":"into a very public spotlight."},{"time":565322,"text":"Because after all,"},{"time":566499,"text":"the ban on women in combat\nwas still very much in place."},{"time":570856,"text":"And at her funeral,"},{"time":572294,"text":"the head of Army Special Operations came,\nand gave a public testimony"},{"time":576722,"text":"not just to the courage of Ashley White,"},{"time":578961,"text":"but to all her team of sisters."},{"time":581746,"text":"\"Make no mistake about it,\" he said,\n\"these women are warriors,"},{"time":586198,"text":"and they have written a new chapter\nin what it means to be a female"},{"time":589538,"text":"in the United States Army.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":592989,"text":"Ashley's mom is a teacher's aide\nand a school bus driver,"},{"time":596691,"text":"who bakes cookies on the side."},{"time":599340,"text":"She doesn't remember much\nabout that overwhelming set of days,"},{"time":602546,"text":"in which grief -- enormous grief --"},{"time":605339,"text":"mixed with pride."},{"time":607359,"text":"But she does remember one moment."},{"time":609913,"text":"A stranger with a child\nin her hand came up to her"},{"time":613343,"text":"and she said, \"Mrs. White,"},{"time":616049,"text":"I brought my daughter here today,"},{"time":618371,"text":"because I wanted her to know\nwhat a hero was."},{"time":622490,"text":"And I wanted her to know\nthat heroes could be women, too.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":627749,"text":"It is time to celebrate\nall the unsung heroines"},{"time":631387,"text":"who reach into their guts"},{"time":633136,"text":"and find the heart and the grit\nto keep going and to test every limit."},{"time":638100,"text":"This very unlikely band of sisters\nbound forever in life and afterward"},{"time":643844,"text":"did indeed become part of history,"},{"time":646190,"text":"and they paved the way for so many\nwho would come after them,"},{"time":649345,"text":"as much as they stood on the shoulders\nof those who had come before."},{"time":654303,"text":"These women showed that warriors come\nin all shapes and sizes."},{"time":659454,"text":"And women can be heroes, too."},{"time":662648,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":663824,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}